### Decision Engine API Tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/health

###

### Domain Schema
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/domain/schema

###

### Start Session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "external_user_id": "demo-user-1"
}

###

### Test 1: Greeting
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "replace-with-session-id",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "external_message_id": "dev-cli-001",
  "text": "Привет"
}

###

### Test 2: Request operator
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "replace-with-session-id",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "external_message_id": "dev-cli-002",
  "text": "Хочу поговорить с оператором"
}

