### Test 12: Long conversation history test
# First message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "replace-with-session-id",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "external_message_id": "dev-cli-011",
  "text": "Привет"
}

###

# Follow-up message in the same session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "replace-with-session-id",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "external_message_id": "dev-cli-012",
  "text": "У меня вопрос по услугам"
}

###

# Continue conversation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "replace-with-session-id",
  "channel": "dev-cli",
  "external_message_id": "dev-cli-013",
  "text": "Какие услуги вы предоставляете?"
}

